title: Audio commander

----------_Audio commander_---------- 
___________________________________________

Audio commander is a app with wich 
you can easely change the master
volume, wave volume, SW synth volume,
CD Player volume, PC beep volume,
Line in volume, Stereo Mix volume,
Microphone volume,.....
Audio commander has an integrated 
Audio recorder, Graphic Equalizer,
and a lot more.....(and looks cool...)
